        <abstract>
            <p>CD has spoken to Hooker of JS’s scientific merit, but has not suggested him for a colonial appointment.</p>
            <p>Advice on style of writing.</p> 
<p>Making extensive extract of JS’s orchid paper to communicate to Linnean Society [<hi rend="italic">J. Linn. Soc. Lond. (Bot.)</hi> 8 (1865): 162–7].</p> 
